TO TALK TO ME.

75
00:02:50,587 --> 00:02:53,048
YOU'RE A SMART COOKIE,
YOU WILL.

76
00:02:53,131 --> 00:02:54,383
(BOTH LAUGH)

77
00:02:54,466 --> 00:02:55,884
HEY, SAV!

78
00:02:55,968 --> 00:02:58,220
