LIKE I'M SOME SORT OF CRIMINAL!

83
00:03:05,018 --> 00:03:07,938
WHICH IS WHY I CAN'T LET YOU
BACK ON THE AIR.

84
00:03:08,021 --> 00:03:10,649
WHAT?! I THOUGHT YOU SAID
I WAS GREAT!

85
00:03:10,732 --> 00:03:12,442
REMEMBER?
FUNNY, CONTROVERSIAL?

86
00:03:12,526 --> 00:03:13,694
YEAH,
BUT THERE'S A FINE LINE

87
00:03:13,777 --> 00:03:16,238
BETWEEN CONTROVERSIAL
AND OFFENSIVE.

88
00:03:16,321 --> 00:03:17,656
A LOT OF PEOPLE ARE PISSED,
MAN.

89
00:03:17,739 --> 00:03:19,032
ESPECIALLY YOUR CO-HOST.

90
00:03:19,116 --> 00:03:22,578
YOU-YOU CAN'T SILENCE ME
'CAUSE I HAVE AN OPINION!

91
00:03:22,661 --> 00:03:24,371
ALL RIGHT,
I'M GOING TO SIMPSON.

92
00:03:24,454 --> 00:03:25,831
(SCOFFS)

93
00:03:25,914 --> 00:03:27,499
YEAH, GO TO SIMPSON.

94
00:03:27,583 --> 00:03:29,084
BUT I WAS THE ONE
WHO CALMED HIM DOWN.

95
00:03:29,168 --> 00:03:31,295
SIMPSON WANTED YOU
SUSPENDED!

96
00:03:31,378 --> 00:03:33,505
SI-

97
00:03:33,589 --> 00:03:34,798
SO YOU'RE CANCELLING
THE SHOW?

98
00:03:34,882 --> 00:03:36,508
SAV:
NO.

99
00:03:36,592 --> 00:03:38,385
WE'RE NOT CANCELLING THE SHOW,

100
00:03:38,468 --> 00:03:41,638
YOU'RE JUST NOT HOSTING
ANYMORE.

101
00:03:43,182 --> 00:03:44,892
AND ADAM IS?!

102
00:03:45,893 --> 00:03:48,437
SO THAT'S HOW IT IS?!

103
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,230
ALL RIGHT.

104
00:03:50,314 --> 00:03:51,690
GLOVES OFF!
DAVE.

105
00:03:51,773 --> 00:03:53,108
(BELL RINGS)

106
00:03:55,903 --> 00:03:59,406
FIONA:
SO MY MOM WENT COMPLETELY
MAMA BEAR ON ME FOR SKIPPING.

107
00:03:59,489 --> 00:04:00,407
APPLY MYSELF AT SCHOOL,

108
00:04:00,490 --> 00:04:01,909
OR IT'S BACK TO NEW YORK
I GO.

109
00:04:01,992 --> 00:04:03,410
WHERE'D YOU TAKE OFF TO,
ANYWAY?

110
00:04:03,493 --> 00:04:05,579
I JUST HUNG OUT
WITH CHARLIE.

111
00:04:05,662 --> 00:04:06,914
AHA!

112
00:04:06,997 --> 00:04:09,333
WE'RE JUST FRIENDS,
HOLLY J.

113
00:04:09,416 --> 00:04:10,918
FOR NOW.

114
00:04:11,001 --> 00:04:12,252
AT LEAST, WE WERE.

115
00:04:13,253 --> 00:04:14,254
SHE STILL HASN'T CALLED ME BACK

116
00:04:14,338 --> 00:04:17,049
SINCE MY MOM LOST IT
IN FRONT OF HER.

117
00:04:17,132 --> 00:04:18,300
WHAT IF SHE DOESN'T?

118
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:20,219
WELL THEN, SHE'S NOT
A FRIEND WORTH HAVING.

119
00:04:20,302 --> 00:04:21,428
BESIDES, YOU'RE WORRYING
TOO MUCH ABOUT HER.

120
00:04:21,512 --> 00:04:23,305
YOU SHOULD BE KEEPING
YOUR PROMISE TO YOUR MOM.

121
00:04:23,388 --> 00:04:24,306
I WILL,

122
00:04:24,389 --> 00:04:26,350
ONCE I KNOW THAT EVERYTHING'S
OKAY WITH CHARLIE.

123
00:04:26,433 --> 00:04:28,519
IF SHE'S NOT CALLING
YOU BACK...

124
00:04:28,602 --> 00:04:31,021
THEN I SHOULD GO TALK
TO HER IN PERSON!

125
00:04:31,104 --> 00:04:33,565
HOLLY J:
THAT'S NOT WHERE I WAS GOING
WITH THAT AT ALL!

126
00:04:33,649 --> 00:04:35,234
(LOCKER SLAMS)

127
00:04:35,317 --> 00:04:36,652
DAVE:
HEY, THANKS FOR COMING!

128
00:04:36,735 --> 00:04:38,737
YOU GUYS ARE FREEDOM FIGHTERS.

129
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:40,447
HERE, PUT THESE ON.

130
00:04:43,033 --> 00:04:44,535
THESE ARE DRESSES.

131
00:04:44,618 --> 00:04:46,912
WHY ARE WE...
CONNOR, WAIT A SECOND!

132
00:04:46,995 --> 00:04:47,996
DAVE:
NO, PUT IT ON!

133
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,456
LOOK, WE'RE GONNA DRESS UP
LIKE GIRLS,

134
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:52,501
HEAD INTO THE GIRLS WASHROOM,
AND YOU KNOW, GO.

135
00:04:52,584 --> 00:04:54,211
WHAT?! WHY?

136
00:04:54,294 --> 00:04:55,462
TO PROVE A POINT!

137
00:04:55,546 --> 00:04:56,922
LOOK, JUST 'CAUSE YOU'RE DRESSED
UP AS THE OPPOSITE SEX

138
00:04:57,005 --> 00:04:58,966
DOESN'T GIVE YOU THE RIGHT
TO USE THEIR WASHROOM.

139
00:04:59,049 --> 00:05:00,676
ALL RIGHT?
HURRY UP!

140
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,094
CONNOR:
I NEED A DIFFERENT SIZE.

141
00:05:02,177 --> 00:05:03,428
TAKE IT OFF!

142
00:05:03,512 --> 00:05:05,222
OKAY,
HOW IS THIS A GOOD IDEA?

143
00:05:05,305 --> 00:05:06,515
LOOK, I SPOKE THE TRUTH
ON THE RADIO

144
00:05:06,598 --> 00:05:08,517
AND GOT SILENCED!

145
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,602
ALL RIGHT,
IT'S UNFAIR, WES!

146
00:05:10,686 --> 00:05:12,354
YOU GET THAT,
RIGHT?

147
00:05:13,355 --> 00:05:14,940
WE'RE TAKING A STAND,
COME ON!

148
00:05:15,023 --> 00:05:17,651
I CAN'T, DAVE.
I'M SORRY.

149
00:05:21,029 --> 00:05:22,656
NOT YOU, TOO!

150
00:05:27,411 --> 00:05:28,412
YOU'RE A BUNCH
OF CHICKENS!

