YOUR STUPID JUNK!

227
00:08:40,103 --> 00:08:41,313
NO, YOU CARE ABOUT
BEING A CRYBABY

228
00:08:41,396 --> 00:08:42,564
UNTIL YOU GET
THE ONLY ACTUAL GUY

229
00:08:42,648 --> 00:08:45,275
ON THE RADIO SHOW
KICKED OFF!

230
00:08:45,359 --> 00:08:47,361
(DAVE HALF LAUGHS)

231
00:08:48,362 --> 00:08:52,115
YOU KNOW, PEOPLE KNOW
YOU'RE NOT A DUDE, ADAM.

232
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:55,911
DAVE:
OOF!

233
00:08:56,912 --> 00:08:58,455
HUH? WHAT?

234
00:08:58,539 --> 00:09:01,124
GUY:
NOW, HEY! HEY! HEY!

235
00:09:01,208 --> 00:09:02,501
(DAVE AND ADAM GRUNT)

236
00:09:02,584 --> 00:09:05,546
